sailpoint.integration

Class TraceExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • sailpoint.integration.AbstractIntegrationExecutor
      • sailpoint.integration.TraceExecutor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    sailpoint.integration.IntegrationExecutor, IntegrationInterface

    public class TraceExecutor
extends sailpoint.integration.AbstractIntegrationExecutor
    Implementation of IntegrationExecutor interface used for system testing. This prints information to stdout and keeps role and provisioning information in memory.
